			<tr>
				<td><font face="verdana" size="1">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<a href="/quests/default.asp">Quests</a><br>
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tline.gif">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<a href="default.asp?land=1152">Kelethin</a><br>
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tline3.gif">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<b>Trueshot Longbow</b><br><br>
				</td>
			</tr>
				
			<tr>
			<td>
				<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="3"><b>    Trueshot Longbow</b>&nbsp;<a href="../Subscribe.asp?DID=1950"><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></font>
					<br>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">
					<b><a href="mailto:maximus@stny.lrun.com">Kyodai</a> | 
		                        1/9/2000 12:13:09 PM</b></font></p>
					
					<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">Maesyn Trueshot, of the Champions of Faydark, gives you a pouch and tells you to find the 4 ingredients to make a Trueshot Longbow. You need: <BR>
Dwarven Wire from Trantor Everhot in Kaladim<BR>
Treant Wood from Jyle Windshot in Freeport<BR>
Microservos from spiders in the Ak'Anon area<BR>
Spiderling silk from any spiderling<BR>
<BR>
Put them in the pouch, combine, and give to Maesyn Trushot
			<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p>
					</p>
			</td>
			</tr>
